🧠 Token-level Prediction and Saliency

This visualization encodes multiple token-level metrics using color and styling:

  • 🎨 Background color: token saliency (darker = more salient)
  • 📏 Border thickness: prediction loss (thicker = higher loss)
  • 🔲 Border color: token prediction probability

Color thresholds for prediction probability:

  • 🔴 Red: prob ≤ 0.0004
  • 🟡 Yellow: 0.0004 < prob ≤ 0.0022
  • 🟢 Green: prob > 0.0022
